<title>USA: TABLE- Emcor Q2 net shr $0.09 VS $0.93.</title>
<headline>TABLE- Emcor Q2 net shr $0.09 VS $0.93.</headline>
<dateline>NORWALK, Conn. 1997-08-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>Second quarter ended June 30</p>
<p>				1997			1996</p>
<p> Shr			  $0.09		    $0.93</p>
<p> Net			    0.9			9.2</p>
<p> Revs			 475.6		    387.7</p>
<p>Six months</p>
<p> Shr			  $0.11		    $0.56</p>
<p> Net			    1.1			5.6</p>
<p> Revs			 909.4		    770.4</p>
<p>(All data above in millions except per share numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE: Emcor Group Inc's earnings for the 1997 quarter and 1997 six months include a $1.0 million charge for retiring debt, or $0.10 a share.</p>
<p>Without the charge, Emcor would have reported $0.19 a share for the 1997 quarter and $0.21 a share for the 1997 six months.</p>
<p>The 1996 quarter earnings include a net gain of $8.1 million from selling its Jamaica Water Supply Co.</p>
<p>The 1996 six month earnings include the net $8.1 million gain and a $4.8 million net charge.</p>
<p>The company had 9.4 million shares outstanding as of April 30.</p>
